SELECT 
    id, 
    title, 
    concat('https://idyoveanwiuwcvgxijtz.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/eagle-images/', storage_path) as imageUrl
FROM eagle_images
WHERE 
    title ILIKE '%lake%' OR title ILIKE '%door%' OR title ILIKE '%threshold%'
    OR EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM unnest(tags) AS tag WHERE tag ILIKE '%lake%')
    OR EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM unnest(tags) AS tag WHERE tag ILIKE '%door%')
    OR EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM unnest(tags) AS tag WHERE tag ILIKE '%threshold%')
ORDER BY created_at DESC, random()
LIMIT 3
